values: （用于疑问句、条件从句）任何人；无论谁；（同 anyone）

bilingual.target: 贾米尔不想让任何人来。

bilingual.source: You can be anybody on any kind of ship you like.
bilingual.target: 你可以是任何船上的任何人。

bilingual.source: It is an art project open to anybody, anywhere in the world.
bilingual.target: 这是一个向世界上任何地方的任何人开放的艺术项目。
任何人都可以成为朋友。
你认识这里的任何人吗？
任何人都能学会这项技能。
任何人都可以参加这个活动。

bilingual.source: Theophile looked sad and dreamy, and didn't talk with anybody else.
bilingual.target: 西奥菲勒看上去悲伤而恍惚，不和任何人说话。

bilingual.source: I can't focus my attention on anything and don't even feel like talking to anybody.
bilingual.target: 我不能把注意力集中在任何事情上，甚至不想和任何人说话。

list.abstract: anybody是一个英语单词，可以用作代词，可以翻译为任何人、无论谁，等等。

yingyinNormal.en: I promise we won't tell anybody. No.
yingyinNormal.zh: 我保证不会告诉任何人的。不行。
yingyinNormal.videoNameEn: 《Night at the Museum: Secret of the Tomb》

yingyinNormal.en: I'll go. I'll do anything with anybody.
yingyinNormal.zh: 我去。我愿意和任何人一起做任何事。

yingyinNormal.en: I would never let anybody grow up like that.
yingyinNormal.zh: 我绝对不会让任何人在这种环境中成长的。

yingyinNormal.en: Maya isn't influenced by anybody. are you? Whatever you say.
yingyinNormal.zh: 玛雅没被任何人影响，对吧？随你怎么说。

yingyinNormal.en: No, I didn't tell anybody that I knew you. Why not?
yingyinNormal.zh: 不，我没告诉任何人我认识你。为什么？

yingyinNormal.en: Oh, no. This is not my fault. I'm not blaming anybody.
yingyinNormal.zh: 这不是我的错。我没有在指责任何人。

yingyinNormal.en: A familial match. So the killer could be anybody in that kid's family.
yingyinNormal.zh: 家族联系，这么说凶手可以是这孩子家族的任何人。

yingyinNormal.en: Remember what I told you, Forrest. You're no different than anybody else is.
yingyinNormal.zh: 记住我说的话，福雷斯，你和其它任何人是一样的。

yingyinNormal.en: I just don't want him to meet anybody until I am over my crush. And I will get over it.
yingyinNormal.zh: 在我结束对他的暗恋之前，我不要他跟任何人约会，我会忘记他的。

yingyinNormal.en: No, Anna. I belong here, alone, where I can be who I am, without hurting anybody.
yingyinNormal.zh: 不，安娜，我属于这里。孤单一人，只有在这里，我才不会伤害到任何人。

yingyinNormal.en: No, Anna. I belong here, alone, where I can be who I am, without hurting anybody.
yingyinNormal.zh: 不，安娜，我属于这里。孤单一人，只有在这里，我才不会伤害到任何人。

yingyinNormal.en: You didn't tell anybody I was, did you? No. I'll be right back. You. Take a lot of pictures.
yingyinNormal.zh: 你没有告诉任何人我怀孕了吧？没有，我马上回来，你，多拍一些照片。

yingyinNormal.en: You're right. Monica, I'm so sorry. It's an honest mistake. It could happen to anybody. See you.
yingyinNormal.zh: 你说的对，我很抱歉，这是出自好意的误会。可能发生在任何人身上的，再见。

yingyinNormal.en: The garden erupted, and to do it on the national stage, Anybody who saw that moment will never forget.
yingyinNormal.zh: 整个球馆都沸腾了，在这样一个全国瞩目的舞台任何人看过之后都永生难忘

yingyinNormal.en: Have you looked at the loan-level data? I mean, they're giving these loans to anybody with a credit score and a pulse.
yingyinNormal.zh: 你看过发放贷款的数据吗？任何人只要有信用评分都能随意拿到贷款。

yingyinNormal.en: He didn't want anybody to see him but he'd be drunk so he'd stumble, crash into something and wake everybody up.
yingyinNormal.zh: 他不想被任何人发现，可是他醉得摇摇晃晃，然后撞东撞西，把大家都吵醒。

yingyinNormal.en: Yeah. We promised we weren't gonna tell anybody this, but about a month ago, Rachel and I slept together. And?
yingyinNormal.zh: 对，我们答应不会告诉任何人，但是，大约一个月前，瑞秋跟我上床。结果呢？

yingyinNormal.en: Listen, Adrienne, you can't tell Chandler about this. Oh, believe me, Ross, I won't be telling anybody about this.
yingyinNormal.zh: 听着，安卓，你可不能告诉钱德。哦，相信我，罗斯，我不会告诉任何人的。

yingyinNormal.en: So, who do you have to schmooze to get this deal? I'm not gonna schmooze anybody. I'm gonna let my work speak for itself.
yingyinNormal.zh: 你得拍谁的马屁，才能得到这份工作？我不会拍任何人的马屁，我的工作成果足以说明一切。

yingyinNormal.en: It was the result of a unique approach to life I believe almost anybody can adopt. It starts with embracing reality and dealing with it.
yingyinNormal.zh: 而是因为独特的处事方式，我相信任何人都能学会。我们要从拥抱和处理现实开始。

direction_info.description:
数据源自2012-2023年12年间全国考研试卷，由搜狗翻译进行大数据分析汇总，数据仅供参考。

<highlight> 考频分布</highlight>
由搜狗翻译收集历年真题试卷、汇总单词出现的总频次、释义分布。题型选自2012-2023年全国考研英语一和考研英语二共24套考研试卷，包括阅读、完型填空、翻译、写作等所有题型。

<highlight> 考纲释义</highlight>
精选全国考研考纲词汇、单词义项，由搜狗大数据与考纲、历年真题进行匹配。

<highlight>真题例句</highlight>
精选2012-2023年12年间全国考研英语一和考研英语二试卷，由搜狗大数据与搜索内容匹配历年真题例句。

搜狗翻译拥有最终解释权。

disambiguation_list.sense_disambiguation: 表示“某人；有人”，通常用在肯定句中。
表示“某人；有人”时，通常用在否定句或疑问句中；还可以表示“任何人”，可以用在肯定句中。
